<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 03:23:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尽管获得亚军，全黑队主教练罗伯逊仍“很高兴”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/all-blacks-coach-robertson-pleased-despite-runners-up-finish-2024-09-29/</link><description>全黑队主教练斯科特·罗伯逊表示，他对球队在橄榄球锦标赛中的表现感到满意，尽管新西兰队获得第二名，未能在他们南半球的纪录中再添第 21 个冠军头衔。</description><pubDate>Sun, 29 Sep 2024 02:43:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/all-blacks-coach-robertson-pleased-despite-runners-up-finish-2024-09-29/</guid></item><item><title>王宣扬中国作为和平缔造者的角色，呼吁中东停火</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/wang-touts-chinas-role-peacemaker-calls-mideast-ceasefire-2024-09-28/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周六在联合国大会上寻求提升中国作为全球和平缔造者的信誉，呼吁中东停止战斗，并宣传北京在俄罗斯乌克兰战争问题上的外交努力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 16:00:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/wang-touts-chinas-role-peacemaker-calls-mideast-ceasefire-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>瑞士赞扬中巴乌克兰和平计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/switzerland-praises-china-brazil-peace-plan-ukraine-2024-09-28/</link><description>瑞士外交部表示支持中国主导的旨在结束乌克兰战争的和平计划，并于周六表示其对此类努力的看法已发生重大变化，基辅表示这一立场令人失望且不合逻辑。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 15:20:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/switzerland-praises-china-brazil-peace-plan-ukraine-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>上海证券交易所延迟交易后进行测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shanghai-stock-exchange-run-test-after-transaction-delay-2024-09-28/</link><description>据国营《证券时报》周六报道，中国上海证券交易所将于周日对其拍卖平台和其他多个平台进行测试，一天前，交易发生了不明原因的延迟。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 11:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/shanghai-stock-exchange-run-test-after-transaction-delay-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，欧盟将于 10 月 4 日投票最终确定对中国制造的电动汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-vote-oct-4-finalize-tariffs-china-made-evs-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-28/</link><description>据彭博社周六援引知情人士消息称，欧盟计划于 10 月 4 日就是否对中国制造的进口电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税进行投票。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 07:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-vote-oct-4-finalize-tariffs-china-made-evs-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>中美会谈后在南海举行军演</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-military-drills-south-china-sea-after-talks-with-us-2024-09-28/</link><description>周六，在中国最高外交官与美国同行讨论缓解地区紧张局势的方法数小时后，中国军方表示，中国空军和海军部队正在南海争议地区进行演习。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 04:04:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-holds-military-drills-south-china-sea-after-talks-with-us-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国与亚太国家在南海举行联合海上演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-australia-japan-new-zealand-hold-joint-maritime-activity-south-2024-09-28/</link><description>周六，五国武装部队在南海部分海域举行联合海上演习，而中国则在有争议的水道进行了自己的军事演习。</description><pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 01:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-australia-japan-new-zealand-hold-joint-maritime-activity-south-2024-09-28/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，币安创始人赵被美国释放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-founder-zhao-released-us-custody-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-27/</link><description>据彭博社援引美国监狱管理局发言人的消息报道，币安创始人赵长鹏已于周五从加州一所惩教所获释。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 22:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-founder-zhao-released-us-custody-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>与中国会面后，布林肯表示北京关于乌克兰和平的言论“站不住脚”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-chinas-wang-meet-un-sidelines-2024-09-27/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯在周五与中国外交部长王毅的会谈中强调了美国对中国支持俄罗斯国防工业基础的强烈担忧，称北京关于乌克兰和平的言论“不合常理”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 17:39:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-chinas-wang-meet-un-sidelines-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>尽管泽连斯基愤怒，中国和巴西仍继续推进乌克兰和平计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-brazil-press-with-ukraine-peace-plan-despite-zelenskiys-ire-2024-09-27/</link><description>周五，中国和巴西继续努力召集发展中国家支持一项结束俄罗斯乌克兰战争的计划，尽管乌克兰总统泽连斯基否认该倡议符合莫斯科的利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 17:14:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-brazil-press-with-ukraine-peace-plan-despite-zelenskiys-ire-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟改变氢能项目拍卖规则以限制中国的存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-changes-hydrogen-project-auction-rules-limit-chinese-presence-2024-09-27/</link><description>周五公布的新条款显示，欧盟宣布修改氢补贴拍卖规则，以限制欧盟在可再生能源供应链中对中国的依赖。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 14:51:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-changes-hydrogen-project-auction-rules-limit-chinese-presence-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对俄罗斯在中国生产攻击无人机的报道感到担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-concerned-by-report-russia-producing-attack-drones-china-2024-09-27/</link><description>欧盟发言人周五表示，有关俄罗斯正在为乌克兰战争开发中国支持的攻击无人机计划的报道“令人深感担忧”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 13:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-concerned-by-report-russia-producing-attack-drones-china-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国降低短期借贷成本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-borrowing-cost-standing-lending-facility-2024-09-27/</link><description>中国央行周五晚间表示，将常备借贷便利（SLF）所有期限的借贷成本降低了 20 个基点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 12:42:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cuts-borrowing-cost-standing-lending-facility-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>一系列刺激措施推动中国相关股票上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-linked-stocks-climb-bevy-stimulus-measures-2024-09-27/</link><description>在美国上市的中国企业和专注于中国的基金股票周五大幅上涨，并有望在推动世界第二大经济体经济增长的一系列激进刺激措施的最新推动下继续强劲上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 12:16:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-linked-stocks-climb-bevy-stimulus-measures-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>日本称中国海军航母在太平洋停留7天</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navy-carrier-spotted-pacific-seven-days-japan-says-2024-09-27/</link><description>日本防卫省周五表示，过去7天在太平洋发现中国海军“辽宁”号航母。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 10:14:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navy-carrier-spotted-pacific-seven-days-japan-says-2024-09-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>